ZH: 我始终相信努力一定会有回报。
EN: I always believe that hard work will pay off.

ZH: 她始终对他保持着深深的感情。
EN: She has always held deep feelings for him.

ZH: 我始终坚持自己的梦想，从未放弃。
EN: I have always persisted in my dreams and never give up.

ZH: 他始终未能达到他父母的期望。
EN: He has always failed to meet his parents' expectations.

ZH: 她始终都是一个独立自主的女性。
EN: She has always been an independent woman.

ZH: 我始终记得那个特殊的日子。
EN: I always remember that special day.

ZH: 无论发生什么事情，家人始终都是我的支持者。
EN: No matter what happens, my family is always my supporters.

ZH: 在这个过程中，始终要注重细节。
EN: In this process, attention to detail is always important.

ZH: 不论工作多忙，他始终保持积极的态度。
EN: No matter how busy he is at work, he always maintains a positive attitude.

