EN: Let us always be loyal to our values.

ZH: 始终相信自己，你可以做到任何事情。
EN: Always believe in yourself, you can achieve anything.

ZH: 在困难时期，我们始终保持团结。
EN: During difficult times, we always stay united.

ZH: 始终要对别人保持尊重和友善。
EN: Always treat others with respect and kindness.

ZH: 不论成功与否，我们始终要保持谦虚。
EN: Regardless of success or failure, we should always remain humble.
